Gerber Kawasaki | Life Insurance









































Gerber Kawasaki








Life Insurance


The life insurance process can be very confusing, yet it is an integral part of your overall financial plan. Due to the fact many life insurance companies have their own sales agents, it is difficult to truly compare which policy is best for you.
As independent financial advisors who specialize in life insurance planning, we offer a comprehensive review of your situation and provide you with objective solutions to meet your family needs. We hold your hand through every step of the insurance process from choosing a life insurance company, picking an affordable premium and benefit, deciding which type of policy is best suited for you. Contact us for a complimentary consultation with one of our advisors.


Have questions about protecting your family?
Speak to an Advisor


Try our Insurance Calculator to find out how much life insurance you need.





How much Life Insurance do I need?
This question is unique to each family. We determine the amount of insurance each family needs based off many factors including your current income, liabilities and the number of children you have. We know that cost is one of the most important factors in picking a life insurance policy and benefit amount. With that in mind, we will customize a plan that will not only fit into your budget, but also provide the benefit you need to protect your family.


What type of Life Insurance should I get?
Navigating through a sea of insurance policies and the agents that come with them is a daunting task. Let us simplify the process and explain to you exactly what you need to know. There are two main types of life insurance: temporary, or term, insurance and permanent insurance. We will help you choose the policy that is right for you.












Gerber Kawasaki | Gerber Kawasaki Wealth and Investment Management









































Gerber Kawasaki








Sports Group




At Gerber Kawasaki, we believe that athletes deserve to have a team dedicated to conflict-free advice. We help athletes in not only building their financial plan, but working with their agents, publicists, accountants, managers to make sure they are taken care of on all angles. As many athletes play on a team, we ensure you have the right financial team in place for your situation. It is crucial that every player on YOUR team is working for YOU.
Our team is led by Elijah, Ben and Malcolm.  Being involved and around sports most of our lives, we understand the challenges athletes face.  Our athlete program is competitive at its core and focuses on all the challenges an athlete will go through in his or her career.



Join Sports Group








Malcolm Jones (Co-Director)

An athlete from a young age, Malcolm graduated high school as the Gatorade National Player of the Year. While playing running back at University of California Los Angeles, Malcolm earned his degree in economics. As a former athlete himself, Malcolm understands the triumphs and tribulations that go along with an athlete's path to success.




Elijah Souza (Co-Director)

Growing up playing sports his whole life, Elijah has been engulfed in sports culture from a young age. While in college, he led marketing and promotional activities during Loyola Marymount University sporting events. He now works with athletes at all different stages of their careers and helps them through the unique challenges they face.




Ben Dunbar (Co-Director)

Ben has more of an action sports background, growing up with surfing, skateboarding, and skiing all being regular parts of his daily life. With the growing success of events like the X-Games and increasing popularity of extreme sports, Ben helps his athletes take advantage of high incomes at a young age, and building a brand that will last.




Budgeting and Cash Management

"You can live like a king for a year or you can live like a prince for life!"  We will work with you to help you find a balance between saving for your future and enjoying your hard earned money today.  We help you create a budget for during your sports career that can sustain you throughout your life, not just during your playing years.





Investment Management

We often see athletes who have been taken advantage of by advisors who do not put their interest first. At Gerber Kawasaki Wealth Management we legally have a fiduciary responsibility to put our clients best interest first!





Financial Planning

A majority of athletes will make most of their income within the first handful years of their professional careers.  Our job is to help ensure those funds last well beyond retirement from professional sports.





Our Mission

The mission of our Sports Group is to help overcome the unique challenges faced by athletes and help them make sound financial decisions to ensure their wealth lasts long after retirement from professional sports.





